> What is the purpose of studying history?

> How does focusing on Historical Thinking Skills, Historical Reasoning Processes, and AP Themes help us truly study history instead of just trying to memorize stuff?

> What are the Historical Thinking Skills?
Developments and Processes, Sourcing and Situation, Claims and Evidence, Context, Connections, Argumentation

> What are the Historical Reasoning Processes?
Compare and Contrast, Cause and Effect, Continuity and Change Over Time

> What are the AP Themes?
Social, Political, Interactions with the Environment, Cultural, Economic, Technological